                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20 Defense (M) Brazil/328: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-03-17T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >March 17, 1942—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>671. Your 871 of March 14. Firestone and Goodyear will not continue to act, as
                    Rubber Reserve will deal directly with Bank of Brazil.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
